Indonesia although restoring the Indonesian economy appeared
difficult in the short term.
</P>
<P>
Mahathir said Goh and other members of the Singapore delegation
were briefed during the meeting on the steps taken by Malaysia to
overcome the economic downturn in the country such as the proposed
establishment of the National Economic Action Council (NEAC).
</P>
<P>
Malaysia, Indonesia, Thailand, the Philippines and even
Singapore have been affected by the current economic crisis
triggered by speculative attacks on the regional currencies.
