Goh is also scheduled to make an official visit to Malaysia
later.
</P>
<P>
Mahathir visited Indonesia last Saturday and held talks with
President Soeharto on the regional economic crisis.
</P>
<P>
Prior to the Mahathir-Soeharto meeting, Goh also met Soeharto
in Jakarta.
</P>
<P>
Indonesia and Malaysia as well as Thailand, the Philippines and
Singapore, all ASEAN members, have been affected by the regional
currency crisis resulted from speculative attacks on the regional
currencies since last July.  
</P>
