remain the two most favored, attracting half of the applicants.
</P>
<P>
The applicants will have to pass the entrance examinations on
April 5 and 6, and those passed through will have to study for
three to four years before acquiring their desired degrees.
</P>
<P>
Last year, China's inland universities recruited a total of 125
Macao residents for post-graduate and doctorate degree study.
