<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 20 (Xinhua) -- The composite Stock Index on the
Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,203.71 today, down 9.41
points from the previous session, according to the Guangfa
Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
The SSE-30 Index, based on 30 blue chips that are selected from
the more than 300 A shares for domestic investors on the Shanghai
Stock Exchange, closed at 3,871.00, down 51.56 points from the
previous session.
</P>
