<TEXT>
<P>
ZAGREB, January 19 (Xinhua) -- Croatian Foreign Minister Mate
Granic met his Slovenian counterpart Boris Frlec on Monday on
improving bilateral ties and enhancing cooperation.
</P>
<P>
